name: Pink Fuji
description: Reproduction of the work “Mount Fuji as seen from Kashiwabara” (1897) by Kasumasa Ogawa, made using an overlay of shadows in half tone over colors painted with digital brushes.  The image of “Mount Fuji as seen from Kashiwabara” is distributed under CC0 license.  1000x800 JPEG          tw @elis3000
